      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This session rounds up our discussion of causal thinking for policy evaluation. We revisit some of the most notorious threats to internal and external validity by example and explore them interactively case by case&lt;/p&gt;
